00:01:04,438 --> 00:01:07,373
Umrao. Umrao.

14
00:01:09,110 --> 00:01:10,270
Kakve su vesti?

15
00:01:14,281 --> 00:01:15,373
Zasto ne govoris?

16
00:01:17,451 --> 00:01:18,611
Je li vest losa?

17
00:01:19,587 --> 00:01:22,420
Ne tako losa, ali nije ni dobra.

18
00:01:23,290 --> 00:01:24,621
Pa govori onda!

19
00:01:27,027 --> 00:01:28,494
Dogodila se prepirka izmedju
oca i sina.

20
00:01:29,630 --> 00:01:33,964
Stvar je dosla do tog nivoa, da je
Gospodin Nawab razbastinio svog sina..

21
00:01:34,034 --> 00:01:36,969
..svog bogatstva, imovine..

22
00:01:37,037 --> 00:01:42,100
..a mozda, mozda
cak i svog doma.

23
00:01:43,043 --> 00:01:44,169
Ali zasto?

24
00:01:45,379 --> 00:01:48,974
Nawab Sultan je bio nepopustljiv
braneci ljubav prema tebi..

25
00:01:49,049 --> 00:01:52,246
..a njegovom ocu se to 
nedopada, ni malo!

26
00:02:03,397 --> 00:02:04,659
Ostavi me samu.

27
00:02:40,534 --> 00:02:41,626
Dobrodosli.

28
00:02:45,239 --> 00:02:47,707
Jesi li sigurna da ce Nawab
Sultan doci?

29
00:02:47,775 --> 00:02:50,107
Khanum sahib, ovo je Nawab Faiz Ali.

30
00:02:52,179 --> 00:02:54,170
Pozdrav. Molim vas sedite.

31
00:02:55,549 --> 00:02:56,709
Prvo vi sedite.

32
00:03:02,723 --> 00:03:04,247
Zaboga, cemu to oruzje?

33
00:03:04,325 --> 00:03:08,193
Da? Oh! Razumem.

34
00:03:08,262 --> 00:03:12,062
Ali ja sam cuo, kada se zapuca
u bordelu..

35
00:03:12,132 --> 00:03:16,262
..taj bordel postane popularniji.

36
00:03:18,205 --> 00:03:23,268
Ali vi budite sigurni, ni jedan metak
nece biti ispaljen iz mog oruzja.

37
00:03:25,145 --> 00:03:28,740
Dobro, zaboravite oruzje.
Dajte mi vas zglob.

38
00:03:31,218 --> 00:03:35,416
Naredite, ciju lepotu
preferirate iz naseg bordela?

39
00:03:35,489 --> 00:03:36,820
Umrao Jaan.

40
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:42,358
Umrao Jaan, zar mi neces
ponuditi beetle list?

41
00:03:51,171 --> 00:03:54,607
Pohvale na racun mladosti
Umrao Jaan, su me dovele ovamo.

42
00:03:54,675 --> 00:03:59,840
Khanum sahib. Reci mu, da ja
necu biti u stanju da mu budem drustvo.

43
00:04:01,715 --> 00:04:06,175
Ja pripadam Nawab Sultanu.
I ostajem verna njemu.

44
00:04:07,288 --> 00:04:10,121
Jeste li culi? Moj Bog mi
ne dozvoljava da govorim lazi..

45
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:12,852
..cak smo i mi nemocni
pred njenom vernoscu.

46
00:04:13,193 --> 00:04:16,788
Za sada, srecan sam
sto sam video Umrao Jaan.

47
00:04:17,197 --> 00:04:18,323
Pozdrav.

48
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:23,201
Gospodine Faiz Ali. Mi ovde
imamo i drugih lepotica,

49
00:04:23,270 --> 00:04:26,262
Khursheed, Bismillah, Husna, Zeenat,

50
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:27,807
Mozete izabrati bilo koju.

51
00:04:28,208 --> 00:04:34,340
Ali ne. Moja rdjava sudbina je,
da volim jedino Umrao Jaan.

52
00:04:36,216 --> 00:04:37,877
A Umrao voli nekoga drugog.

53
00:04:39,486 --> 00:04:46,824
Ali ja nisam tuzan. Ako zivot
ostane lojalan, srescemo se jos.

54
00:04:53,467 --> 00:04:57,801
Za blistavost Umrao Jaan, i
vrednost vaseg vremena.

55
00:04:59,239 --> 00:05:00,331
Hvala.

56
00:05:03,677 --> 00:05:07,909
Dozvolila si Faiz Ali-u
momenat pred tvojim stopalima.

57
00:05:08,782 --> 00:05:10,477
Veoma, veoma hvala za to.

58
00:05:12,586 --> 00:05:13,712
Dovidjenja.

59
00:05:15,756 --> 00:05:16,848
Dovidjenja.

60
00:05:29,670 --> 00:05:33,436
On je neposten, ali
bogat je momak.

61
00:05:34,742 --> 00:05:35,868
Nazdravimo za Nawab Sujjat Ali-a.

62
00:05:47,221 --> 00:05:48,415
Pocuj me.

63
00:05:52,393 --> 00:05:53,451
Idi.

64
00:05:54,561 --> 00:05:55,823
Odmah se vracam.

65
00:06:03,303 --> 00:06:05,237
Da te pitam, ovaj ljubitelj skitanja..

66
00:06:05,305 --> 00:06:06,863
..dokle ce on sedeti ovde
piti alkohol?

67
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:08,601
Pricaj tise, cuce te.

68
00:06:08,675 --> 00:06:11,644
Neka cuje, zar
da brinemo o tome?

69
00:06:11,712 --> 00:06:14,840
Ja ti kazem, ne mogu
to vise da podnesem.

70
00:06:14,915 --> 00:06:17,907
Begum, on je moj prijatelj,
pokusaj da razumes.

71
00:06:17,985 --> 00:06:19,247
Onda ti sacuvaj to prijateljstvo!

72
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:22,311
A dozvoli meni da napustim
ovu kucu i odem.

73
00:06:22,389 --> 00:06:25,916
Nema potrebe da ti ides.
Daj mi samo malo vremena.

74
00:06:29,329 --> 00:06:35,632
Ashraf Miyan. Vodi me kod Umrao.

75
00:06:41,842 --> 00:06:44,777
Ti. I to u ovo vreme? Nadam se
da je sve u redu?

76
00:06:48,749 --> 00:06:49,875
Pio sam alkohol.

77
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:54,780
Popio sam previse.

78
00:07:00,694 --> 00:07:04,960
Zar neces da me udaris?
- Zasto tako kazes?

79
00:07:05,899 --> 00:07:10,359
Insistirao je da ga vodim kod Umrao
Jaan, pa sam ga i doveo ovde.

80
00:07:12,372 --> 00:07:14,806
Dobro si ucinio. Hvala.

81
00:07:16,577 --> 00:07:17,839
Gospodine Nawab ce ostati sa mnom.

82
00:07:20,647 --> 00:07:21,807
Vidi. Dodji.

83
00:07:35,395 --> 00:07:39,991
Ja sam beskucnik, ali
nisam onesposobljen.

84
00:07:44,404 --> 00:07:45,530
Hajde..

85
00:07:46,607 --> 00:07:47,665
Hajde.

86
00:08:06,493 --> 00:08:08,518
Da li ti to pokusavas da me negujes?

87
00:08:15,903 --> 00:08:18,565
Mislis li da je ovo prvi put
da sam pijan?

88
00:08:27,714 --> 00:08:29,545
Nisam samo danas pijan.

89
00:08:35,856 --> 00:08:38,689
Kako bese ghazal?

90
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:46,793
'Pogledaj me, da bih mogla da te pozdravim'.

91
00:08:50,404 --> 00:08:51,598
Pozdravi me..

92
00:08:53,574 --> 00:08:55,098
Sta to govoris?

93
00:08:56,743 --> 00:08:59,940
Ti si moja kruna.
- Kruna!

94
00:09:04,484 --> 00:09:07,817
Bez kuce. Bez posla.

95
00:09:09,556 --> 00:09:12,491
Siromasan. Kruna.

96
00:09:16,530 --> 00:09:18,589
Zar nisi mogla da nadjes nikoga
drugog za salu?

97
00:09:20,834 --> 00:09:24,895
Za Bozju ljubav, nemoj tako
da govoris. - Zasto?

98
00:09:27,507 --> 00:09:29,600
Ne verujes mi
da sam beskucnik.

99
00:09:33,513 --> 00:09:35,777
Idi, i pitaj mog oca.

100
00:09:40,721 --> 00:09:42,916
Nawab Sultan Ali Khan.

101
00:09:53,533 --> 00:09:58,470
Kada mi je bilo 4 meseca..
namokrio sam njegovo krilo..

102
00:09:58,538 --> 00:10:01,996
..a on me je podigao i bacio
me na pod.

103
00:10:08,548 --> 00:10:11,642
Pa sta ako me je izbacio
iz svog zivota, nista strasno.

104
00:10:15,889 --> 00:10:16,981
Da, ima jedna stvar..

105
00:10:21,795 --> 00:10:24,628
Hoces li me ti izbaciti
iz svog zivota?

106
00:10:26,633 --> 00:10:27,827
Sta to pricas?

107
00:10:29,836 --> 00:10:31,599
Moj zivot si ti.

108
00:10:36,677 --> 00:10:39,578
Ja tebe volim i vise od svog zivota.

109
00:10:43,583 --> 00:10:45,676
Ali ako bi bila neverna.

110
00:10:52,092 --> 00:10:54,060
Onda, zapamti jednu stvar..

111
00:10:56,663 --> 00:11:00,599
Ovaj Pathan ce te odseci i odbaciti
od svog zivota.

112
00:11:05,005 --> 00:11:08,270
U redu, odseci me i odbaci.

113
00:11:10,610 --> 00:11:11,907
Ali zasto govoris tako?

114
00:11:12,612 --> 00:11:16,742
Bice sve u redu. Tvoj
otac ce te prigrliti.

115
00:11:23,724 --> 00:11:27,558
Neverovatno. Ja ovde govorim
o nasoj ljubavi..

116
00:11:27,627 --> 00:11:29,720
..a ti o mom ocu.

117
00:11:43,009 --> 00:11:45,273
Da li je to zato sto osecas 
sazaljenje prema meni?

118
00:11:47,914 --> 00:11:49,745
Ja sam ta koja je vredna sazaljevanja.

119
00:11:51,651 --> 00:11:53,175
Kako bih ja mogla da 
sazaljevam druge?

120
00:11:59,726 --> 00:12:03,753
Okreni se ovamo. 
Dozvoli da vidim u tvojim ocima.

121
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:11,835
Mogu jasno da vidim...Sazaljenje.

122
00:12:16,610 --> 00:12:17,804
Sazaljenje.

123
00:12:22,082 --> 00:12:24,710
I to prema tvom robu.

124
00:12:29,222 --> 00:12:30,280
Rob.

125
00:12:40,767 --> 00:12:48,139
Mesto roba nije
ovde.. Ovde je.

126
00:12:49,843 --> 00:12:55,713
Sta to radis? Budi
ovde, pored mene.

127
00:13:00,253 --> 00:13:06,817
Ne. Ja sam tvoj rob.
- Slusaj.

128
00:13:10,730 --> 00:13:14,791
Kakva je ovo detinjastost?
Dodji ovamo. Dodji na krevet.

129
00:13:14,868 --> 00:13:18,395
Hajde.. Hajde gore.

130
00:13:24,744 --> 00:13:28,111
Ali ja.. sam rob od Umrao Jaan.

131
00:13:32,018 --> 00:13:33,144
Rob.

132
00:13:37,757 --> 00:13:41,955
Onda sam i ja tvoj rob.
I ja cu sedeti ovde.

133
00:13:47,767 --> 00:13:50,793
U redu. Onda cemo
spavati ovde.

134
00:13:55,775 --> 00:14:01,077
Dobro, spavaj ovde.

135
00:14:20,066 --> 00:14:21,226
Izvoli Khanum. Hoce li izgledati lepo?

136
00:14:21,801 --> 00:14:23,098
Khursheed, pogledaj ovo.

137
00:14:23,169 --> 00:14:25,228
Koliko je fin vez?

138
00:14:25,305 --> 00:14:28,900
Veoma fin, i veoma lep.
Lpeo ce ti stajati.

139
00:14:28,975 --> 00:14:31,944
Ma'am pogledajte ovo.
- Ne. To nije lepo.

140
00:14:32,012 --> 00:14:36,278
Pokazite mi drugi.
- Uzmite ovaj.

141
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:42,411
Pokazite mi onaj ispod.
Taj ljubicasti.

142
00:14:47,928 --> 00:14:49,088
Pogledajte ovaj vez.

143
00:14:49,162 --> 00:14:50,959
Pokazite mi najskuplji.

144
00:14:53,099 --> 00:14:55,192
Pozovi ovamo Nawab Sultana.

145
00:14:55,268 --> 00:14:56,326
Uzmite ovaj.

146
00:15:00,941 --> 00:15:02,101
Ovaj ne zelim.

147
00:15:08,848 --> 00:15:11,316
Pozdrav, Gospodine Nawab Sultan. Pridjite.

148
00:15:13,053 --> 00:15:14,213
Sedite pored mene.

149
00:15:16,456 --> 00:15:19,118
Sada sam saznala da 
ste nocas stigli ovde?

150
00:15:19,192 --> 00:15:21,524
Bog zna, vase zdravlje
nije bilo dobro.

151
00:15:21,861 --> 00:15:23,192
Kako ste sada?

152
00:15:23,263 --> 00:15:26,858
Dobro sam.
- Neka vas Allah odrzi zdravim uvek.

153
00:15:26,933 --> 00:15:30,061
Ali sta se dogodilo?
- Ne, nista posebno.

154
00:15:30,971 --> 00:15:32,802
Neka je vest u vazduhu..

155
00:15:32,872 --> 00:15:35,932
..da ste imali prepirku
sa starijim Gospodinom Nawab

156
00:15:38,912 --> 00:15:41,278
Gospodine Nawab, takve se
stvari dogadjaju po domovima.

157
00:15:41,348 --> 00:15:43,213
Nemojte da uzmete za uvredu 
sto tako govorim.

158
00:15:44,317 --> 00:15:45,807
I koliko ja znam..

159
00:15:45,885 --> 00:15:49,377
..svo bogatstvo je u rukama
starijeg gospodina Nawab.

160
00:15:49,990 --> 00:15:51,821
Kada god on pozeli
moze biti darezljiv..

161
00:15:51,891 --> 00:15:53,415
..i kada god pozeli, on
moze sklopiti dlanove.

162
00:15:53,493 --> 00:15:56,257
Ali, Khanum sahab..
- Nemoj da se mesas.

163
00:15:58,164 --> 00:16:00,064
Objasnjavala sam mu
svetovne cinjenice.

164
00:16:00,133 --> 00:16:02,465
Moj Bog mi je zabranio da govorim
lazi, Gospodine Nawab.

165
00:16:03,503 --> 00:16:05,994
Bogati ljudi, kao vi,
kurtizanama daju status.

166
00:16:06,072 --> 00:16:09,064
Ali, koja je vrednost
siromasne kurtizane?

167
00:16:09,142 --> 00:16:12,009
Ako se zaljubi,
sta ce onda jesti?

168
00:16:12,078 --> 00:16:15,536
Kurtizana ima samo jednog rodjaka,
a to je bogatstvo.

169
00:16:17,017 --> 00:16:18,279
Govorite istinu.

170
00:16:19,919 --> 00:16:23,252
Khanum sahib, Nawab Sultan ima..
- Opet se mesas?

171
00:16:24,424 --> 00:16:27,154
Dobro zaboravite ovaj razgovor. 
Pogledajte,ovo su marame.

172
00:16:27,227 --> 00:16:29,855
Ako budete velikodusni, 
zbog vas cu..

173
00:16:29,929 --> 00:16:35,060
..po ove stare dane,
mozda kupiti maramu.

174
00:16:35,135 --> 00:16:37,933
Budala je stavila
cenu od 5000..

175
00:16:38,004 --> 00:16:41,440
Sad mi vi recite, gde ja
da nadjem toliku sumu?

176
00:16:41,508 --> 00:16:42,941
Pozdrav.

177
00:16:44,010 --> 00:16:45,500
Gospodine Faiz Ali! Pozdrav.

178
00:16:45,945 --> 00:16:47,469
Dodjite, sedite.

179
00:17:02,062 --> 00:17:05,896
Khanum sahib, ako gledate u mene
zbog marame..

180
00:17:05,965 --> 00:17:07,899
..onda se ne stidim da kazem..

181
00:17:07,967 --> 00:17:10,026
..da nemam novac kod sebe.

182
00:17:10,103 --> 00:17:13,630
Pitanje sramote je za vecinu 
Nawab-a iz Awadha.

183
00:17:14,074 --> 00:17:17,441
Moja sreca! Ja sam sada
postavljena o ovo stanje!

184
00:17:17,510 --> 00:17:21,606
Da za ovakvu jednu maramu, moram
da se zalazem kod tako bogatih ljudi!

185
00:17:27,487 --> 00:17:30,320
Uzmi ovu ogrilcu. Nju mi je darovao
Nawab Sultan licno!

186
00:17:30,390 --> 00:17:32,984
Uzmi, i kupi maramu.

187
00:17:34,994 --> 00:17:36,256
Ona govori lazi.

188
00:17:38,531 --> 00:17:40,089
Ja joj nisam darovao tu ogrlicu.

189
00:17:46,206 --> 00:17:49,039
Nawab Sultan, vi ste
nas najdrazi gost.

190
00:17:49,109 --> 00:17:51,942
Mozete ostati ovde
koliko god zelite..

191
00:17:52,011 --> 00:17:54,946
..ali ako neko kaze da,
tako bogat Nawab..

192
00:17:55,014 --> 00:17:56,948
..prezivljava zbog
velikodusnosti kurtizane..

193
00:17:57,016 --> 00:17:59,678
..onda da zavucem kandze
u njihovo lice?

194
00:18:00,286 --> 00:18:04,245
Ja se izvinjavam, ali ova stvar
predugo traje.

195
00:18:10,363 --> 00:18:14,026
Uzmite ovo. I predajte maramu
Khanum sahib.

196
00:18:14,100 --> 00:18:18,127
A da, kupicu jos jednu..
za Umrao Jaan.

197
00:18:20,373 --> 00:18:24,139
I ako vas dve zelite,
kupicu i za vas.

198
00:18:29,149 --> 00:18:30,309
Ja sada zelim da idem.

199
00:18:34,220 --> 00:18:36,984
Ali pre nego sto ode, zelim da kazem..

200
00:18:37,056 --> 00:18:39,991
..da merenjem ljubavi
skalom za bogatstvo..

201
00:18:40,059 --> 00:18:43,392
..niste samo mene uvredili,
vec citavo covecanstvo.

202
00:18:46,599 --> 00:18:49,329
Izgleda da niste navikli na
stvarnost, Gospodine Nawab.

203
00:18:53,173 --> 00:18:57,007
Ipak, stvarnost je takodje,
Khanum sahib..

204
00:18:57,076 --> 00:19:00,637
..da sam ja Nawab Sultan, a
vi ste vlasnica bordela.

205
00:19:18,198 --> 00:19:21,565
Gde ces? Stani.

206
00:19:30,109 --> 00:19:31,542
I ja cu poci sa tobom.

207
00:19:34,380 --> 00:19:37,747
Ne, Umrao. Ne mozes poci sa mnom.

208
00:19:40,186 --> 00:19:42,120
Ostaces ovde i cekaces me.

209
00:19:46,392 --> 00:19:48,053
Sa ljudima koji te zlostavljaju..

210
00:19:48,127 --> 00:19:50,288
..ne mogu da ostanem ni momenat.

211
00:19:50,363 --> 00:19:52,456
Pa ces tako uvecati moje
poteskoce?

212
00:19:55,134 --> 00:19:57,261
Kako stvari stoje, ja lutam
po pustinnji.

213
00:20:06,212 --> 00:20:07,770
Pokusaj da razumes, Umrao.

214
00:20:10,250 --> 00:20:12,081
Ne mogu da se borim sa celim svetom..

215
00:20:12,151 --> 00:20:13,812
..a ne moze se ni izbrisati sto 
je zapisano u sudbini.

216
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:19,615
